<p>The namespace is already <code>AppBundle\Api</code> - so that's perfect. This holds data for
an <code>application/problem+json</code> response. It has properties for <code>type</code>, <code>title</code> and
<code>statusCode</code> - these being the three <em>main</em> fields from the spec.</p>
