<h2 id="using-apiproblem">Using ApiProblem <a class="headerlink" href="api-problem-class#using-apiproblem" title="Permalink to this headline"><i class="fa fa-link" aria-hidden="true"></i></a></h2>
<p>Let's use this back in <code>ProgrammerController</code>. Start with
<code>$apiProblem = new ApiProblem()</code>. The status code is 400, the type is <code>validation_error</code>
